org.kiji.schema
Interface KijiMetaTable

All Superinterfaces:
Closeable, KijiTableKeyValueDatabase<KijiMetaTable>, KijiTableLayoutDatabase
All Known Implementing Classes:
HBaseMetaTable
@ApiAudience.Framework
@ApiStability.Evolving
@Inheritance.Sealed
public interface KijiMetaTable
extends Closeable, KijiTableLayoutDatabase, KijiTableKeyValueDatabase<KijiMetaTable>

The Kiji meta data table, which stores layouts and other user defined meta data on a per-table basis. Instantiated in KijiSchema via Kiji.getMetaTable()

See Also:
KijiSchemaTable, KijiSystemTable
